%N A396322 Expansion of e.g.f. exp(x)*(cosh(x)-1)*(sinh(x)-x).
%C A396322 Number of ternary sequences of length n with a positive even number of 0's, an odd number >= 3 of ones and no restriction on the number of 2's.
%H A396322 <a href="/index/Rec#order_06">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (8,-22,20,11,-28,12).
%F A396322 a(n) = (3^n - (-1)^n)/4 - (n + 2)*2^(n-2) + n for n >= 2.
%F A396322 G.f.: 2*x^5*(5 - 10*x + 3*x^2)/((1 - 3*x + 2*x^2)^2*(1 - 2*x - 3*x^2)). - _Stefano Spezia_, May 24 2026
%e A396322 For n=7, the 266 strings are the 35 permutations of 0000111, the 21 permutations of 0011111 and the 210 permutations of 001122.
%t A396322 LinearRecurrence[{8, -22, 20, 11, -28, 12}, {0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 10, 60, 266}, 31] (* _Amiram Eldar_, May 23 2026 *)
